===Catch/en
`If the selected phrase is mouse, toggle whether the mouse is caught.`
name: choice()
caught: ∆ (name)? ⊥ … (name = 'mouse') & ~caught
`Every second, move the mouse`
place:  ∆ time(1000ms) ? Place(0m 0m 0m) … caught ?Place(0m 0m)Place(random(-2 2) · 1m random(-2 2) · 1m)

Verse([
		💬(
			"🐭" 
			selectable: ⊤
			place: place
rest:caught?Pose(tilt:180°)Pose()
			move: caught ? Pose() Sequence({0%: Pose(tilt: 0°) 100%:Pose(tilt: 360°)})
			duration: 1s
			name: 'mouse'
		)
	] 
	place: Place(0m 0m -2m)
	frame: Rectangle(-3m 3m 3m -3m)
)